Description: SecuBox TURN/STUN Server Management
 TURN/STUN server management interface for SecuBox WebRTC.
 Features:
  - coturn service control (start/stop/restart)
  - User management with turnadmin integration
  - Temporary credential generation (HMAC)
  - Active session monitoring
  - Configuration editor
  - Three-fold architecture (Components/Status/Access)
